        "text": "committed to develop a Digital Fairness Act that includes legislative proposals, we urge the European Commission to consider our messages below.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s3",
          "section_path": [
            "Identification of legal gaps. Do we need a Digital Fairness Act?"
          ],
          "span": null,
          "chunk_quality": "ok",
