      {
        "para_id": "p40",
        "items": [
          {
            "topic": "Advertising Codes Of Practice",
            "topic_source": "new",
            "evidence_quotes": [
              {
                "quote": "codes of practice"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "meta": {
          "skipped": false,
          "skip_reason": null,
          "validation_ok": true,
          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 10467,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "Self-regulation is an instrument that complements legislation, through setting and enforcing codes of practice, and promoting legal, decent, honest and truthful advertising. It thus fosters consumer trust and a level playing field among competitors. Self-regulation should therefore be promoted wherever possible.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s7",
          "section_path": [
            "Self-regulation"
          ],
          "span": null,
          "chunk_quality": "ok",
          "chunk_word_count": 41,
          "char_len": 313
        }
      },
      {
        "para_id": "p41",
        "items": [],
        "meta": {
          "skipped": false,
          "skip_reason": null,
          "validation_ok": true,
          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 5803,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "The Commission has announced that a Digital Fairness Act will focus on the protection of vulnerable consumers. It should be considered that the Unfair Commercial Practices Directive (UCPD) already defines and protects vulnerable consumers. Instead of proposing new legislation focus should be on improved guidance to the UCPD as on a more effective Consumer Cooperation Protection Network (CPC Network) and improved supervision of existing and harmonized rules.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s8",
          "section_path": [
            "Vulnerable Consumers and Unfair Commercial Practices Directive"
          ],
          "span": null,
          "chunk_quality": "ok",
          "chunk_word_count": 67,
          "char_len": 461
        }
      },
      {
        "para_id": "p42",
        "items": [],
        "meta": {
          "skipped": false,
          "skip_reason": null,
          "validation_ok": true,
          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 5448,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "Cooperation between national authorities and the EU-Commission as well as the cooperation between EU authorities must be improved to ensure consistent application of regulations and authorities having the right technological and digital tools to enforce legislation effectively.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s9",
          "section_path": [
            "Cooperation between national authorities and the EU-Commission"
          ],
          "span": null,
          "chunk_quality": "ok",
          "chunk_word_count": 37,
          "char_len": 278
        }
      },
      {
        "para_id": "p43",
        "items": [],
        "meta": {
          "skipped": false,
          "skip_reason": null,
          "validation_ok": true,
          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 5073,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "We therefore recommend that a new cross-functional task force across the different departments in the Commission is established to ensure enforcement speed, coordination and knowledge-sharing within the Commission and member states. There is a need for a formal structure with a clear mandate and resources to coordinate across member states and ensure enforcement of all relevant consumer protection regulations.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s9",
          "section_path": [
            "Cooperation between national authorities and the EU-Commission"
          ],
          "span": null,
          "chunk_quality": "ok",
          "chunk_word_count": 59,
          "char_len": 413
        }
      },
